\begin_inset space ~
\end_inset


\begin_inset CommandInset citation
LatexCommand cite
key "Deuar2007"

\end_inset

.
 It is generally the case for unitary evolution that errors caused by truncation
 grow in time, leading to a finite time horizon for applicability, as explained
